once the save button entered:

1) check if its existing task
1) if yes hold the task record , and last child record
2)check if the last child task completed
2) if yes - create a child task with next counter and save data to child dataframe
2) if no - update the child id for the parent id

1) if not existing - add a next counter and save data to parent dataframe
2) start from 1 and save data to child dataframe

